Divine Guard
Discworld ritual help
Divine Guard


.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Divine Guard -- Impresses a ritual onto an object to protect it from theft
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Divine Guard stores the power of a single ritual within an object, allowing a priest to
protect it from theft. You need a holy symbol to perform this ritual. After you have
performed this ritual on an item, you will need to "impress" another ritual into it.
.EP

